What is Automatic Crude Fat Analyzer?
Automatic Crude Fat Analyzer is an instrument that automates the standard procedure for determining the fat percentage in a wide variety of raw materials and finished products. By combining efficient solvent extraction, precise measurement of extracted fat, and software‑based data processing, the system delivers rapid, reproducible results without the need for skilled manual handling. The technology is widely adopted in dairy processing plants, feed laboratories, agricultural research facilities, and quality control units across the food industry.

